scheduled_maintenances.name: Contentstack - SSL Certificate Reissue - Scheduled Maintenance

incident_updates.body:
Please be advised that on July 14th, 2025, the Contentstack team will perform a scheduled SSL certificate reissue for *.contentstack.com. No service interruptions are expected during this update.

Customer Action: No action is required unless you are using public certificates for the mentioned URL as hard-coded values in your systems.

		Start: July 14th, 2025, 05:30 AM UTC
		End: July 14th, 2025, 07:00 AM UTC
		Duration: 90 minutes
		Downtime: None expected

Impact: We expect no disruptions in services. If you face any issues while accessing our services, please reach out to Contentstack support at https://www.contentstack.com/customers/support/
